				±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±± CROSS REFERENCE - KEY ENTRY POINTS ±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±

				    seg:off    type	   label
				   ---- ----   ----   --------------------------------
				   2926:0000   far    start

				 ±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±± Interrupt Usage Synopsis ±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±

				        Interrupt 10h : Video display	ah=functn xxh
				        Interrupt 10h :  ah=00h	 set display mode in al
				        Interrupt 10h :  ah=02h	 set cursor location in dx
				        Interrupt 10h :  ah=03h	 get cursor loc in dx, mode cx
				        Interrupt 10h :  ah=05h	 set display page al
				        Interrupt 10h :  ah=09h	 set char al & attrib bl @curs
				        Interrupt 10h :  ah=0Bh	 set color from bx (CGA modes)
				        Interrupt 10h :  ah=0Fh	 get state, al=mode, bh=page
				        Interrupt 10h :  ax=1102h  load	8x8 font, bl=block
				        Interrupt 10h :  ax=1130h  get font type bh info into
				        Interrupt 13h : Disk  dl=drive #  ah=func xxh
				        Interrupt 13h :  ah=04h	 verify	sectors with mem es:bx
				        Interrupt 21h : DOS Services  ah=function xxh
				        Interrupt 21h :  ah=06h	 special char i/o, dl=subfunc
				        Interrupt 21h :  ah=09h	 display char string at ds:dx
				        Interrupt 21h :  ah=0Ch	 clear keybd buffer & input al
				        Interrupt 21h :  ah=1Ah	 set DTA(disk xfer area) ds:dx
				        Interrupt 21h :  ah=27h	 random	block read, FCB @ds:dx
				        Interrupt 21h :  ah=28h	 random	block write FCB @ds:dx
				        Interrupt 21h :  ah=2Ah	 get date, cx=year, dh=month
				        Interrupt 21h :  ah=2Bh	 set date, cx=year, dx=mon/day
				        Interrupt 21h :  ah=2Ch	 get time, cx=hrs/min, dx=sec
				        Interrupt 21h :  ah=2Dh	 set time, cx=hrs/min, dx=sec
				            2 Ocurrences of non-standard interrupts used (search for ??).

				 ±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±± I/O Port Usage Synopsis  ±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±±

				        Port 20h   : 8259-1 int	command
				        Port 20h   :  al = 20h,	end of interrupt
				        Port 42h   : 8253 timer	2 spkr
				        Port 43h   : 8253 timer	control
				        Port 61h   : 8255 port B, read
				        Port 61h   : 8255 B - spkr, etc
				        Port 201h  : start game	1-shots
				        Port 3C0h  : EGA attributes
				        Port 3C0h  :  al = 10h,	mode control
				        Port 3D4h  : CGA/EGA reg index
				        Port 3D4h  :  al = 9, max raster address
				        Port 3D5h  : CGA/EGA indxd data
				        Port 3DAh  : CGA/EGA vid status
				        Port 3DAh  : VGA feature contrl

